'''二高氯酸氧钒'''也称'''高氯酸钒(IV)酰'''，是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为VO(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。它可由V(OH)<sub>4</sub>和3.5 N高氯酸反应得到。<ref>Tishchenko, A. F.; Golub, A. M. Formation of vanadium(IV) perchlorate. ''Izvestiya Vysshikh Uchebnykh Zavedenii, Khimiya i Khimicheskaya Tekhnologiya'', 1974. 17 (5): 656-658. ISSN: 0579-2991.</ref>它的五水合物可溶于水，在水中解离为[VO(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>5</sub>]<sup>2+</sup>和ClO<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup>。<ref>Sathyanarayana, D. N.; Patel, C. C. A physicochemical study of vanadyl perchlorate pentahydrate. ''Indian Journal of Chemistry'', 1965. 3 (11): 486-489. ISSN: 0019-5103.</ref>它可以和{{le|甲基苯基亚砜|Methyl phenyl sulfoxide}}形成配合物VO(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·4MPSO。<ref>Agarwal, R. K.; Singh, Pitam; Singh, Lakshman. Synthesis and characterization of oxovanadium(IV) complexes of methyl phenyl sulfoxide. ''Revue Roumaine de Chimie'', 1993. 38 (7): 853-858. ISSN: 0035-3930.</ref>它可用于制备其它VO<sup>2+</sup>化合物。<ref>Agarwal, Ram K.; Singh, Lakshman; Sharma, Deepak K.; Singh, Ritu. Synthesis, spectral and thermal investigations of some oxovanadium(IV) complexes of hydrazones of isonicotinic acid hydrazide. ''Turkish Journal of Chemistry'', 2005. 29 (3). 309-316. ISSN: 1300-0527.</ref>

